<paragraph role="heading" id="hd_id3150202" xml-lang="en-US" level="2" l10n="U" oldref="10">Fill Format Mode</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3155531" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="CHG" oldref="12"><ahelp hid="HID_TEMPLDLG_WATERCAN">Turns the Fill Format mode on and off. Use the paint can to assign the Style selected in the Styles and Formatting window.</ahelp></paragraph>
